0.body: AkumaKodo (Pronounced: Ah-Ku-Ma Code Oh) is a discord deno bot framework written in TypeScript and deno. It is designed to be a modular and extensible framework that extends the functionality of the deno runtime. It is designed to be easy to use while maintaining a high level of performance and function programming workflow. The framework is build on discordeno version 13.0.0-rc18
